      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p>Liferay Portal Enterprise Edition (EE) is only supported under the following configurations:</p>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 700px; float: left;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><strong>Type</strong></span></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 388px; vertical-align: middle;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><strong>Certified</strong></span></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 388px; vertical-align: middle;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><strong>Supported</strong></span></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 122px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Application Server</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 169px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">JBoss 5.1 EAP</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">JBoss 7.1 AS**</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Glassfish v3.1</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Tcat 6.4</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Tomcat 7.0</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Tomact 6.0</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Weblogic 11</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">WebSphere 7.0</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">WebSphere 8.5</font></span></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 219px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<ul>\n<li><font size=\"2\">JBoss 6.0 EAP**</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">JOnAS 5.2</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Resin 4</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">tcServer 2.6</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Tomcat 8.0 (6.1 EE GA3 Portal-65+)</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Weblogic 10</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Weblogic 10.3</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">WebSphere 6.1****</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">WebSphere 8.0</font></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 122px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Database</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 169px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">DB2 9.7</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Hypersonic (HSQL)</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">MySQL 5.5</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">MySQL 5.1</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Oracle 11.2</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Oracle 10.2</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PostgreSQL 9.0</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PostgreSQL 8.4</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SQL Server 2008 R2</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SQL Server 2005</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Sybase ASE 15.5</span></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 219px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">DB2 10.5</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">MySQL 5.0</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Oracle 11.1</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">SQL Server 2008</font></span></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 122px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Operating System</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 169px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">AIX 7.1</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">AIX 6.1</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">CentOS 6</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">CentOS 5</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Red Hat Enterprise 6</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Red Hat Enterprise 5</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Solaris 10</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Solaris 11</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows 7</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows Server 2008 R2</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows XP</span></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 219px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">HP-UX</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Mac OS X 10.5+</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Oracle Linux 6.1</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Other Linux Distributions</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Ubuntu 11</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Ubuntu 10</font></span></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 122px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Browser*</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 169px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<ul>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Chrome 21</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Firefox 14</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Internet Explorer 9</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Internet Explorer 8</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Safari 5.1</font></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 219px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<ul>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Firefox 3.6</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Internet Explorer 7</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Internet Explorer 6</font></li>\n<li><font size=\"2\">Opera</font></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 122px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">JDK</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 169px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Oracle JRockit 6</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Oracle JDK 7***</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Oracle JDK 6</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Oracle JDK 5****</font></span></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 219px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">IBM JDK 7***</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">IBM JDK 6</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">IBM JDK 5****</font></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">Oracle JDK 8*****</font></span></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> <span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> </span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Certified vs. Supported Environments</span></strong><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">1. Certified: Products in the Certified list have undergone automated regression and certification testing by Liferay and are fully supported with a Liferay Enterprise Subscription.</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">2. Supported: Products in the Supported list have undergone automated regression testing by Liferay and are fully supported with a Liferay Enterprise Subscription.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">*Browser support exclusions:</span></strong><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">1. Versions of browsers that were released after a major Liferay version release have not been tested and support for these newer browser releases will be provided as a commercially reasonable effort only and may be included in subsequent service releases at Liferay’s discretion.</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">2. Versions of browsers that were supported with an initial release of a Liferay version that have reached the end of their product lifecycle are no longer tested in subsequent service releases and support for those older browser releases will be provided as a commercially reasonable effort only.</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">3. “Quirks mode” for all browsers is not supported.</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">4. Internet Explorer Compatibility modes for all relevant versions are not supported due to poor implementation.</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">5. Limited support shall be provided for Internet Explorer 6 on a case-by-case basis. Internet Explorer 6’s performance limitations prohibit it from running the latest Internet technologies effectively without experiencing performance degradation.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">**JBoss 6.0 EAP and JBoss 7.1 AS</span></strong><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">1. JBoss Domain Mode is not supported with Liferay 6.1 EE.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">***Oracle JDK 7 and IBM JDK 7</span></strong><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">1. Oracle JDK 7 and IBM JDK 7 are only compatible with Liferay 6.1 EE GA2 and Liferay 6.1 EE GA3.</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">2. Websphere 8 does not support Oracle JDK 7.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">****Oracle JDK 5, IBM JDK 5, and Websphere 6.1</span></strong><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">1. Oracle JDK 5, IBM JDK 5, and Websphere 6.1 are not supported with Liferay 6.1 EE GA3.</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"></span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">***** Oracle JDK 8</span></strong><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">1. Oracle JDK 8 is compatible with 6.1.20+ and a JDK 8 compatible app server. </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.liferay.com/documents/10182/246659966/Liferay+Portal+6.1+EE+Compatibility+Matrix.pdf/ad71b0f8-ae58-5bd2-9f73-71fa8ae1252e?t=1584747455496\" target=\"_self\">Download PDF</a></p>"
      },
